Package: blue-archive-waydroid
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Blue Archive Linux Team (minhmc2007) <https://github.com/minhmc2007/Blue-Archive-Linux>
Description: Automated installer for Waydroid, Google Play, and Blue Archive.
 This package automates the setup of Waydroid on Debian-based systems. It handles
 kernel prerequisite checks, network configuration, installation of GAPPS and
 the Houdini translation layer, and finally, the installation of Blue Archive.
 The installation process will begin immediately after the package is installed.
Depends: curl, ca-certificates, gpg, software-properties-common, iptables, dnsmasq, iproute2, git, python3, python3-venv, lsb-release, wget, unzip, sudo
Provides: blue-archive-installer

